<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II., Graf von Wertheim</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die in Graf Johanns Geleit gefangenen und freigelassenen Nürnberger Kaufleute und für die Herausgabe eines Hengstes und bittet um Freilassung auch der anderen Kaufleute und Herausgabe ihrer Ware.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_88" id="43v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_88_r1l1"><expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> . <expan>Graf<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>VVerth<ex>eim</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_88_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / . Als etlıche vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒunde<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> geleitte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l3"><expan>geuange<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd Jn Jr hengſt <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvord<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein / hat vns hans </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l4"><expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> wol geſagt / vvie Jr ew <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> gar <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l5">beweiſet vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ernſt darcʒü getan habt / daʒ Jr etlıch ledıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l6">vnd auch <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hengſt ein teil wider ſein <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . des wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l7"><expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiʒʒe <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ewr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l8">noch dar cʒü wenden / vnd mit ernſt beholffen ſein wöllet / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l9">
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ </del> was <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>awſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſtee </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l10">daʒ die ledig vnd Jn das Jr <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> werde / Als etc / Das <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_88" id="43v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>, <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> czü
                                <expan>Werth<ex>eim</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als etliche unser
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> geleitte
                                <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> und in ir hengst
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein, hat uns Hans
                            <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, wol gesagt, wie ir ew
                                <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> gar
                            <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beweiset und
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ernst darczü getan habt, daz ir etlich
                        ledig und auch <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hengst ein teil wider sein
                                <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, des wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizze
                                <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir ewr gnade noch dar czü wenden und mit ernst beholffen sein wöllet,
                        was <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> sein
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>awsse<ex>n</ex></expan> stee, daz
                        die ledig und in das ir <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> werde, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
